Famous Tanzanian actress Elizabeth 'Lulu' Michael is off the market. She tied the knot on Tuesday with her long-term boyfriend Francis Majizzo. Majizzo is a Tanzanian media mogul and the father of Hamisa Mobetto's first-born daughter, Fancy. The private ceremony, done in Mbezi, Dar es Salaam, was attended by close friends and family members. A source told Word Is the 25-year-old actress has been planning the wedding for months. "They started planning this a long time ago, and the guy was there for her. Even when she was jailed, he stood by her." Lulu spent a year behind bars for manslaughter after the death of her ex-boyfriend and actor, Steven Kanumba.